        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200?text=Dr.+Amit+Deshmukh" alt="Dr. Amit Deshmukh">
        <h2>Dr. Amit Deshmukh</h2>
        <p><strong>Specialty:</strong> Psychiatrist</p>
